Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.14,0:00:04.85,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Reasoning and hints are interlinked,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.85,0:00:06.36,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Allowing us to understand a case's mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.81,0:00:08.32,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Today's case is on the Shinkansen,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.32,0:00:10.03,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}where a very complex case unfolds!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.44,0:00:11.99,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Recognizing that single truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.99,0:00:13.78,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}a child with the intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.78,0:00:15.87,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}His name is: Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.38,0:01:47.10,Title,Sign,0,0,0,,The Bullet Train Transport Case\N(Part One)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.10,0:01:51.06,Character Card,Sign,0,0,0,,New Osaka Station
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.53,0:02:05.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's nothing here...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.74,0:02:07.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.03,0:02:09.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks like your phone's ringing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.62,0:02:14.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder who it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.71,0:02:18.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An unknown caller?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.63,0:02:25.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, could this be a love call from Kudo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.51,0:02:29.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry, hurry! This could be about a date!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.23,0:02:33.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way, it's an unknown caller.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.56,0:02:34.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.48,0:02:36.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop wasting time! Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.15,0:02:41.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now the princess can speak with her knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.53,0:02:44.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.03,0:02:46.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shin'ichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.79,0:02:48.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shin'ichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.20,0:02:51.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shin'ichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.12,0:02:54.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What took you so long?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.92,0:02:56.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Uncle...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.04,0:02:57.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What're you reading?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.67,0:03:01.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.47,0:03:03.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bull's-eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.68,0:03:12.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because it's been so long since you called.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.27,0:03:19.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, how'd you know I was in Osaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.28,0:03:24.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Hattori called me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.16,0:03:30.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hattori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} called you, did he?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.79,0:03:32.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was just by chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.41,0:03:37.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How was the "K3" event, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.51,0:03:45.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see... Which do I want...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.47,0:03:51.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see... Where are the newspapers...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.85,0:03:53.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You have a paper over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.69,0:03:55.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it, Ran?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.77,0:03:59.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, Shin'ichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.82,0:04:02.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have you heard about that case?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.74,0:04:06.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I saw it on the news.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.74,0:04:09.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Ray Curtis case, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.49,0:04:13.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I still can't believe it, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.29,0:04:14.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kudo?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.33,0:04:16.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.88,0:04:19.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually, Shin'ichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.09,0:04:23.96,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I asked him to...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.76,0:04:26.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, you mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.59,0:04:29.64,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The uniform you had Ray sign?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.10,0:04:30.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.51,0:04:34.60,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}You didn't have to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.81,0:04:36.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.31,0:04:42.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Despite everything that's happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.44,0:04:49.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No matter what, Ray will always be my hero on the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.24,0:04:51.53,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Thanks, Ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.33,0:04:57.29,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Well, I have some things I need to look into.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.96,0:05:00.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um... Shin'ichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.42,0:05:08.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you want to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.55,0:05:11.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just exactly how he feels about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.89,0:05:17.52,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.52,0:05:20.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shin'ichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.11,0:05:25.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do it, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}! Do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.16,0:05:35.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shin'ichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.00,0:05:38.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shin'ichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.08,0:05:40.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wanted to know...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.97,0:05:52.09,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10\an8}Attention customers:
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.64,0:05:59.73,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10\an8}The train arriving at #26 is leaving\Nfrom Nozomi for Tokyo at 2:56 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.98,0:06:02.48,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That was the train, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.19,0:06:03.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.36,0:06:06.73,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I'll call you later then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.57,0:06:08.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.24,0:06:10.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.66,0:06:14.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey you, this conversation isn't over yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.55,0:06:17.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That jerk...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.71,0:06:19.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He hung up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.13,0:06:20.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't blame him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.26,0:06:22.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's always busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.05,0:06:23.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What're you doing, Kazuha?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.09,0:06:24.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Heiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.93,0:06:26.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's got you so worked up?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.81,0:06:28.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kudo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} just called...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.43,0:06:31.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But he hung up just when it got good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.56,0:06:33.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It wasn't like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.73,0:06:36.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.02,0:06:36.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.40,0:06:38.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're dealing with love!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.07,0:06:45.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kudo must've hung up to avoid the attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.49,0:06:51.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That guy always does that, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.00,0:06:55.92,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Don't even.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.97,0:07:05.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't hint around at it, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.72,0:07:11.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tell him! Tell him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.61,0:07:18.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't dodge it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.27,0:07:23.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Throw him a fastball, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.74,0:07:30.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it, Ran?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.91,0:07:35.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you planning to play baseball?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.71,0:07:37.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah, kind of...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.29,0:07:40.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, being too direct is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.05,0:07:43.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know that, but it still...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.17,0:07:45.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, hold on...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.72,0:07:48.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.93,0:07:50.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Officer Takagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.56,0:07:58.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're transporting a suspect!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.44,0:08:02.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't go around yelling it, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.36,0:08:05.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, regardless...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.36,0:08:08.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What'd this guy do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.53,0:08:11.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name's Ogura Senzou, a drug dealer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.62,0:08:17.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We tried to get a warrant to arrest\Nhim in Tokyo, but he got away.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.38,0:08:22.30,Character Card,Sign,0,0,0,,Ogura Senzou
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.58,0:08:22.80,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,We then staked out an old house\Nof his in Kansai and got him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.42,0:08:25.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I remember seeing this guy in the paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.34,0:08:29.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They had something about him being\Ntransferred from Osaka to Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.14,0:08:36.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think they found a large cache\Nof drugs at his Tokyo residence.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.14,0:08:36.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.27,0:08:39.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're aiming big here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.15,0:08:43.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We hope he'll give up their ring leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.48,0:08:44.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.40,0:08:45.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.95,0:08:49.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Get me some coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.74,0:08:50.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.58,0:08:53.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would you go get him some, Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.74,0:08:54.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.12,0:08:57.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, make sure it's cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.54,0:09:03.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He could try to do something with hot coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.42,0:09:08.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder if I have change...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.73,0:09:18.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.77,0:09:22.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,These are tickets to Sana Kazumi's magic and illusion show!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.19,0:09:24.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.40,0:09:28.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah, on my next day off.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.66,0:09:32.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}? You're interested in magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.78,0:09:35.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.16,0:09:36.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.91,0:09:42.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} from the traffic department had\Nan extra ticket and asked me to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.00,0:09:46.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yumi, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.38,0:09:49.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I told her I wasn't interested, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.26,0:09:53.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.76,0:09:55.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.76,0:09:57.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Go, have fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.77,0:10:01.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let me know if you can figure out his tricks, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.69,0:10:06.61,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}So, so, how about this...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.44,0:10:11.82,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}You tell Miwako that I asked you on a date.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.87,0:10:17.45,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}If her expression changes, you can get her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.37,0:10:20.83,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}If her expression changes...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.50,0:10:24.42,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Telling a girl like Miwako how you feel directly is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.29,0:10:27.92,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}You have to hint around with her first.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.67,0:10:29.26,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.76,0:10:31.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What're you waiting on, Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.13,0:10:33.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.97,0:10:36.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, we're going back to our seats.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.60,0:10:37.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.81,0:10:41.48,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}As I figured, it didn't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.19,0:10:44.10,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It's no use...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.61,0:10:52.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're almost to Mt. Fuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.07,0:10:53.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.70,0:10:58.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think something happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.45,0:11:01.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.91,0:11:04.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's a case?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.08,0:11:08.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right, I'll go check that bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.75,0:11:10.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You stay here, Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.55,0:11:11.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.64,0:11:24.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, please make way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.31,0:11:26.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.70,0:11:41.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"This is a bomb. Do not touch!"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.54,0:11:44.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How long's it been here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.54,0:11:49.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The last passenger found it, so I'd say it hasn't been too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.59,0:11:51.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.76,0:11:52.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.11,0:12:17.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are a lot of people gathered back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.62,0:12:20.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess something really did happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.37,0:12:22.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.21,0:12:32.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna go take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.55,0:12:34.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.72,0:12:41.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't, it's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.93,0:12:42.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stay still!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.93,0:12:47.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.19,0:12:51.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can I go to the bathroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.73,0:12:57.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've been trying to hold it, but I'm at my limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.32,0:13:01.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, let's wait until Sato{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} gets back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.49,0:13:05.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I told you, I'm at my limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.20,0:13:06.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.20,0:13:08.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I should just go right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.42,0:13:10.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.04,0:13:12.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.84,0:13:16.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.42,0:13:17.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.67,0:13:20.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.50,0:13:21.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The bathroom, the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.76,0:13:34.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How is it, Officer?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.39,0:13:37.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you hear anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.86,0:13:39.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, a ticking noise.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.62,0:13:45.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,First, we'll need to evacuate the passengers.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.37,0:13:47.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have the driver...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.19,0:14:17.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's only a prank.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.69,0:14:21.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The one who found the bag...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.82,0:14:23.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can you give me a statement?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.21,0:14:33.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you done yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.58,0:14:36.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't rush me, Officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.50,0:14:42.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's kinda hard to do this with one hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.39,0:14:45.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.14,0:14:48.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, Officer...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.39,0:14:53.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your partner mentioned me naming\Nwho I got the drugs from earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.35,0:14:56.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's too bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.19,0:15:04.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That I'll soon be a bird that can't sing, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.58,0:15:08.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.41,0:15:13.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.92,0:15:16.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where'd you get this knife!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.84,0:15:23.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I've gotta get Sato{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.30,0:15:25.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's no use!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.10,0:15:29.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We must be in a tunnel!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.93,0:15:32.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.40,0:15:39.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll be right back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.19,0:15:43.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll be right back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.65,0:15:44.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.38,0:16:00.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What'd you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.80,0:16:02.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He stabbed himself in the bathroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.38,0:16:04.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, he had a knife when I opened the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.84,0:16:06.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.22,0:16:09.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How'd he even get a knife!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.76,0:16:14.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-I don't know, I just opened the door and saw blood...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.14,0:16:17.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, come look for yourself, Sato{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.40,0:16:18.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.29,0:16:36.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sato{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, he's in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.04,0:16:36.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.46,0:16:41.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He pulled it out!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.54,0:16:42.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He pulled the knife out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.01,0:16:49.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.14,0:16:52.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's already dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.26,0:16:54.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,N-No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.63,0:17:25.34,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It doesn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.17,0:17:28.30,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This entire scene...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.30,0:17:29.18,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Doesn't add up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.89,0:17:34.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.22,0:17:38.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The suspect committed suicide while\Nyou were transferring him!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.31,0:17:40.85,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}You idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.52,0:17:44.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What the hell were you all thinking!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.15,0:17:47.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, well, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.82,0:17:50.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After I took him to the bathroom,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.61,0:17:52.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I heard him scream.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.20,0:17:57.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After I opened the door, I saw he was already\Ncovered in blood with the knife in hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.29,0:18:05.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To get to Sato{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, I handcuffed him\Nto the safety bar to keep him in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.09,0:18:08.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I decided it was best to make sure he stayed in the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.89,0:18:17.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if he did have a fatal injury, having a dangerous and\Narmed suspect around the passengers would've been bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.68,0:18:22.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And so, by the time Sato{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and I got back,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.23,0:18:25.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he had already removed the knife and died from blood loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.94,0:18:30.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Regardless, I'll send some back-up\Nto meet you at the arrival platform.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.36,0:18:32.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't let anyone near the scene until then!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.57,0:18:34.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.08,0:18:42.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Should a suspect kill himself in the custody\Nof an officer, things would get messy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.13,0:18:45.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A minor suspension,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.92,0:18:47.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,a major suspension,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.59,0:18:48.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,or a loss of benefits.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.17,0:18:50.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.38,0:18:57.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Worst case scenario, they'd get discharged.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.02,0:19:00.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How pitiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.48,0:19:03.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sato{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, you can't say anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.31,0:19:04.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was your responsibility, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.48,0:19:08.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes? Takagi here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.57,0:19:11.53,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Takagi{\rHonorifics - Radio\be10}-kun{\r\be10}, it's me, Yumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.70,0:19:13.86,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Yumi{\rHonorifics - Radio\be10}-san{\r\be10}?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.86,0:19:15.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, how'd it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.91,0:19:20.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know, the ticket of love scheme.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.41,0:19:25.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How'd it go? Did Miwako blush? Did she not react?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.00,0:19:28.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.29,0:19:29.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can trust me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.51,0:19:33.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now is not the time for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.09,0:19:34.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Call me at a better time!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.56,0:19:42.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess it didn't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.18,0:19:44.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.14,0:19:44.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What'd she say?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.94,0:19:48.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, nothing for you to worry about!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.74,0:19:59.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But now you've gotta wonder how he got the knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.41,0:20:03.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, he isn't some magician.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.08,0:20:08.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While being transported and guarded by two\Nofficers, he couldn't possibly conceal a knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.42,0:20:09.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's not a magician...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.17,0:20:12.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's a samurai!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.80,0:20:16.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look at the way the knife is pointing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.68,0:20:18.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For it to fall this way...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.89,0:20:23.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He'd have had to hold it up like this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.06,0:20:26.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means this guy had to pull the knife out...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.35,0:20:29.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like a samurai.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.31,0:20:30.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.40,0:20:32.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.32,0:20:36.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which way was he holding the knife\Nwhen he stabbed himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.11,0:20:41.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course it was backwards. It's easier that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.49,0:20:46.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, he stabbed himself holding it backwards,\Nand switched when he pulled it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.08,0:20:47.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How weird...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.87,0:20:51.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then maybe someone else pulled out the knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.59,0:20:53.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that really possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.13,0:20:57.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The blood is weird, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.93,0:21:07.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look, the blood on the knife and around\Nmost of his body is solid like jelly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.48,0:21:11.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the blood on his hand is liquid...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.56,0:21:13.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One's solid and one's liquid, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.36,0:21:18.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe the blood on his hand isn't really blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.15,0:21:20.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it's definitely the same color...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.53,0:21:22.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Heparin.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.74,0:21:25.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Heparin?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.70,0:21:26.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.83,0:21:29.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If blood were mixed with Heparin...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.13,0:21:33.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You mean it would...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.38,0:21:34.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.50,0:21:38.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After so long, blood hardens and becomes difficult to carry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.72,0:21:42.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, if you were to mix it with heparin and put it in a bag...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.47,0:21:46.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You could smuggle the blood paste onto the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.10,0:21:48.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Blood paste?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.89,0:21:49.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.98,0:21:50.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.06,0:21:57.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If someone were to hide the blood paste and knife\Nin the bathroom beforehand, this would be...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.15,0:22:01.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A murder case.
